{"tid":657023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亮劍] 面對貿戰激烈衝突，人民日報連續6日出馬克思對抗","createTime":"2018-05-07T17:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T10:05:50.000Z","uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5ecddc50a9cb26c169eccbdec36fda8d4547aaff","tid":657023,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>亮劍！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=trvtn1/1ns80003367op739o0sn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dtrvtn1%2F1ns80003367op739o0sn.jpg&h=f7e79c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人民日報最近6日的頭條<br />\n<br />\n5月2號：《他的英名和事業永世長存&mdash;寫在馬克思200周年誕辰之際》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012939_38ccf27d6e13c4b8f4f664c215424e43.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012939_38ccf27d6e13c4b8f4f664c215424e43.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ae37e984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012939_38ccf27d6e13c4b8f4f664c215424e43.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月3號：《紀念馬克思誕辰200週年大會 將於5月4日上午在京舉行 習近平將出席大會併發表重要講話》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012940_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012940_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7f17457f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012940_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月4號：《紀念馬克思誕辰200週年重點圖書在京首發  國際社會積極評價馬克思和馬克思主義的當代意義  馬克思主義依然深刻影響人類發展進程》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012941_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012941_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e5a37715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012941_3496f986bd6201fbab53c032d674e99a.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月5號：《向人類最偉大的思想家致敬 》《紀念馬克思誕辰 200 週年大會在京舉行》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012942_c12d99e1bb106a7b4f70bd5df7ae8a71.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012942_c12d99e1bb106a7b4f70bd5df7ae8a71.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a38d6bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012942_c12d99e1bb106a7b4f70bd5df7ae8a71.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月6號：《馬克思的學說依然閃爍著耀眼的真理光芒 》《為堅持馬克思主義執行而努力》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012944_47d2bde7f816e1acc73f6054fff87756.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012944_47d2bde7f816e1acc73f6054fff87756.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1b1101d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012944_47d2bde7f816e1acc73f6054fff87756.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月7號：《馬克思主義指引中國成功走上康莊大道》《用馬克思主義觀察時代解讀時代引領時代》《紀念馬克思誕辰200週年理論研討會舉行》</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012945_1dc1faa1265d2ee301fd5786bb793a38.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F012945_1dc1faa1265d2ee301fd5786bb793a38.png&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4a307e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/012945_1dc1faa1265d2ee301fd5786bb793a38.png</a>"},{"pid":"07ed88aeeac000d60d4649bd1ace197da66e6a53","tid":657023,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"又玩騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c786a899ab86a17517b3aadd1c44871c319c77","tid":657023,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"支持馬克思<br />\n<br />\n但重停留喺資本主義 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307cf119ebae454486aeff2534d5b5443214c3c4","tid":657023,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/160023_567dd7e739aacd7093b6cb4dd47f4927.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F160023_567dd7e739aacd7093b6cb4dd47f4927.png&h=c2ab5783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月4日，紀念馬克思誕辰200週年大會在北京舉行，習近平發表重要講話。<br />\n<br />\n「馬克思是全世界無產階級和勞動人民的革命導師，是馬克思主義的主要創始人，是馬克思主義政黨的締造者和國際共產主義的開創者，是近代以來最偉大的思想家。」<br />\n<br />\n「馬克思主義極大地推進了人類文明進程，至今依然是具有重大國際影響的思想體系和話語體系，馬克思至今依然被公認為&lsquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">千年第一思想家&rsquo;。」</span>"},{"pid":"e92ad6897e38bef1c253a4207adc8b0f3fff768f","tid":657023,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cc3fbef894fe32635c1a981e9ce5cdbe7c1f7b","tid":657023,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"唔敢寫點畀美國撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8058f9c0d265fd220429fbf02bc27deafde84b42","tid":657023,"uid":34602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"習思想去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae61ee2cf43782999c2c9861942b6b8c435f3d8","tid":657023,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"scor